automatic dagger as part of their preparation to commit the
unlawful act, left Addis Ababa to Dire Dawa on July 20, 1993.
</P>
<P>
The convicts were apprehended while trying to force the
airliner to fly to Djibouti at 9 a.m. on July 26, 1993.
