in the world and China is the most populous developing country, so
it is important that the two countries increase cooperation in
environmental protection.
</P>
<P>
He said that China has opened its doors in the area of
environmental protection and that he hopes the US, with its
experience and advanced technology in environmental protection,
will enhance practical cooperation with China, such as in
improving energy resources and developing environmental protection
industries.
</P>
<P>
Weldon said he hopes the two countries' governments can set up
a coordination group to promote cooperation in environmental
protection. 
