<TEXT>
<P>
BONN, January 24 (Xinhua) -- Peter Graf, father of women's
world tennis queen Steffi Graf, was sentenced Friday to three
years and nine months in prison for tax evasion on the earnings
of his daughter.
</P>
<P>
