<HEADLINE> Vanuatu Prime Minister Ends China Visit </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHENZHEN, January 24 (Xinhua) -- Vanuatu's Prime Minister
Rialuth Serge Vohor wound up a six-day visit to China and left
here for home today.
