<HEADLINE> Zambian Products Enjoy Duty Free in Nordic </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LUSAKA, January 24 (Xinhua) -- Being one of the least
developed countries, Zambia enjoys duty free access of its
industrial products to the Nordic countries.
</P>
<P>
The products include canned beef, canned vegetables, textiles
and leather products, Zambia Daily Mail reported today.
</P>
<P>
This was disclosed at a seminar held here this week. The
seminar is part of a series of workshops and seminars that the
Export Board of Zambia (EBZ) has been organizing to impart
knowledge on export management and to ensure continued dialogues
with exporters and other key players in the promotion of
non-traditional exports of Zambia.
</P>
<P>
EBZ Trade and Information Department Manager Johnson Mwenya
told the seminar that Zambian exporters have potential but need
to export high quality products with right prices if they are to
penetrate these markets. 
</P>
</TEXT>
