remove obstacles hampering foreign direct investment in the
country, the Hindustan Times reported today.
</P>
<P>
Addressing a meeting organized by the Confederation of Indian
Industry, President of the Federation of German Industries
Hans-olaf Henkel said there was an urgent need to do so.
</P>
